<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bù biàn de shǒu hòu 迦南1038</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bù biàn de shǒu hòu bù biàn de xún qiú,
 chuán fú yīn de dào lù shàng wǒ men yī rán yào shǒu wǎn shǒu.
 zhuāng jià fā bái ya, chóu dí zài nù hǒu.
 kào zhe yé sū gāng qiáng zhuàng dǎn, zǒu guò měi yī gè chūn qiū.
 xiàng qián zǒu zāi nán zài hòu tóu.
 zài bù yào yǒu chí yán de shùn fú, chí dào de jiǎo bù.
 jǐng zhōng yǐ jīng qiāo xiǎng, zhèng huí dàng zài quán qiú.
 yǐ yǒu hěn duō rén lí nǐ yuǎn qù, kuài bǎ líng hún qiǎng jiù.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1038</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>